                            </div>
                        </div>

                            <div id='page4' style='display:none'>
                              <p>
          To help you make a choice in each round of the game, you will have access to a recommendation app. You will be able to ‘chat’ with the app by choosing a question from a set of questions that you will be provided with. You submit your question by clicking on the question. The app will in turn respond to your question by providing a suggestion on what to do or a feedback on the game played so far. Chatting with the app to get advice is entirely optional and you are free to decide how often or not to chat with the app. Sometimes, you will also be prompted by the app to seek advice.
          
          <div>
                        <img src="/images/tutorial/imgChat.png" style="display: block;"  class='col-md-12'/>
      </div>
                            </div>

                            <div id='page5' style='display:none'>
                              <p> At the end of the round, the points obtained by both of you will be highlighted for you to see. Your points in each round will depend on your choice and the choice of your opponent. This gives rise to the four possible scenarios as shown in the screenshot below. In each cell, the first number represents your points and second number represents the points of your associate.
                              </p>
          
