              </div>
              <div id='page6' style='display:none'>
                <p> <b>YOUR EARNINGS </b>
                      Your accumulated earnings is obtained by summing your points over all rounds of the game thus far. These points are then converted to money by multiplying each point by $0.01. In the unlikely event that your total earnings at the end of all rounds is negative, it will be ignored (no negative bonus earning is possible).
          
          <p> <b> YOUR FEEDBACK</b>
          At the end of the game, you will be asked to fill a survey regarding your decisions in the game.
                            </div>

                      
